  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sugar-infused oil in a small saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the pitted dates and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the coconut sugar, rose water, almond milk, vanilla extract, and salt to the saucepan.",
